race.description: Follow Thedogssa On X (Pbd N/P) Stake Pr2
race.comment: GOLDEN GANGSTER (1) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 20.06 beating Bulsara. Expected to measure up again. MR. ZING ZANG (8) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at this track over 342m behind It's Jackie (20.42) in a Other. Was in the money the start prior. Worth another chance. ANTECEDENT (7) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 342m behind Kota Lambai (20.51) in a Other. Boasts a strong record from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Should play a prominent role. SMOOTH VIXEN (5) was in the money again last time and not beaten far when third (20.21) at this track in a Other.

runners.name: Mr. Zing Zang
runners.owners: G Pidgeon, M Pidgeon, M Calicchio
